  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK519">
<l>viṉaikkaṇ viṉaiyuṭaiyāṉ kēṇmaivē ṟāka </l>
<l>niṉaippāṉai nīṅkun tiru</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Prosperity will leave (the king) who doubts the friendship of the man who steadily labours in the discharge of his duties.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
